{"tid":125573,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"成人學鋼琴 求老師","createTime":"2017-02-18T15:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T16:41:36.000Z","uid":80499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"850158a65ce4d28ccbb7a47e26d33749c921040c","tid":125573,"uid":80499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:09:10.000Z","msg":"之前去左街坊琴行學琴, 個老師叫我彈細路歌<br />\n<br />\n我連基本拍子都唔識打<br />\n但成日話我升左級想加我錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真心求一個識教大人彈琴的老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夢想係三年內彈琴一首小狗圓舞曲(因為鍾意Chopin 而這首應該最易?)"},{"pid":"1473bffbca02169c2e93c7d81c2a697614266590","tid":125573,"uid":58951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:12:04.000Z","msg":"小狗圓舞曲梗係唔係蕭邦最易啦"},{"pid":"a296a0bab682f67ee054adffb093994c3fc9355c","tid":125573,"uid":57571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:13:18.000Z","msg":"求+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   識彈兒歌就夠"},{"pid":"a59281d31b1657933b765b20f4a40e0cce1088de","tid":125573,"uid":58951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:15:31.000Z","msg":"小狗圓舞曲梗唔係蕭邦嘅最易啦<br />\n你學左幾耐佢話你升左級呀？<br />\n由幾級升到幾級？<br />\n唔識邊彈邊數定唔識睇幾拍？<br />\n識唔識睇譜？"},{"pid":"35c94f0db0fda16e3a0573f59973ba8d15478456","tid":125573,"uid":80499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:24:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小狗圓舞曲梗係唔係蕭邦最易啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁邊首會易d?<br />\n其實我最鍾意係fantaisie impromptu<br />\n但我應該一世都彈唔到<br />\n所以想學首蕭邦最易的歌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">當貼近一下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"714c98eda14da29e8e026e309af5e86c08d91b78","tid":125573,"uid":80499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:27:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小狗圓舞曲梗唔係蕭邦嘅最易啦<br />\n你學左幾耐佢話你升左級呀？<br />\n由幾級升到幾級？<br />\n唔識邊彈邊數定唔識睇幾拍？<br />\n識唔識睇譜？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學左三個禮拜, 姐係三堂<br />\n拍子冇數岩過 唔識睇<br />\n<br />\n睇識譜姐係點? 高音譜號的話, 我識搵返個音符代表鋼琴邊個鍵<br />\n但低音譜號就唔識"},{"pid":"468267f92620494c676cb7d23c65272d6ffbb8bb","tid":125573,"uid":80499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:37:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小狗圓舞曲梗唔係蕭邦嘅最易啦<br />\n你學左幾耐佢話你升左級呀？<br />\n由幾級升到幾級？<br />\n唔識邊彈邊數定唔識睇幾拍？<br />\n識唔識睇譜？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學左三個禮拜, 姐係三堂<br />\n拍子冇數岩過 唔識睇<br />\n<br />\n睇識譜姐係點? 高音譜號的話, 我識搵返個音符代表鋼琴邊個鍵<br />\n但低音譜號就唔識</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry 我講清楚先:<br />\n<br />\n學左三堂<br />\n由初級升到一級<br />\n<br />\n之後過多三堂<br />\n話我升到兩級<br />\n<br />\n但我唔識做拍子 真係上到?"},{"pid":"b05f9ce6d3072cc9bc2864e76b92af8a52308c31","tid":125573,"uid":46352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:43:21.000Z","msg":"多年經驗老師<br />\nWhatsapp me :<span style=\"font-size: small;\">96242891</span>"},{"pid":"7afb1f1dbf802caba3614ba0b7bc4797d9015542","tid":125573,"uid":79114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小狗圓舞曲梗係唔係蕭邦最易啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁邊首會易d?<br />\n其實我最鍾意係fantaisie impromptu<br />\n但我應該一世都彈唔到<br />\n所以想學首蕭邦最易的歌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">當貼近一下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小狗圓舞曲同 fantaisie impromptu都唔易wo, 唔好未學行先學走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人覺得夜曲 第2首唔錯，又唔難又好聽"},{"pid":"ec51396536d0c886a726b78ccdd91eff6e359f02","tid":125573,"uid":38765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小狗圓舞曲梗唔係蕭邦嘅最易啦<br />\n你學左幾耐佢話你升左級呀？<br />\n由幾級升到幾級？<br />\n唔識邊彈邊數定唔識睇幾拍？<br />\n識唔識睇譜？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學左三個禮拜, 姐係三堂<br />\n拍子冇數岩過 唔識睇<br />\n<br />\n睇識譜姐係點? 高音譜號的話, 我識搵返個音符代表鋼琴邊個鍵<br />\n但低音譜號就唔識</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry 我講清楚先:<br />\n<br />\n學左三堂<br />\n由初級升到一級<br />\n<br />\n之後過多三堂<br />\n話我升到兩級<br />\n<br />\n但我唔識做拍子 真係上到?</blockquote><br />\nWhat!? 三堂就升一級？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過多三堂再升二級？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嘩真係身為同行都睇唔過眼<br />\n可以為左錢就咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b1b4bd0808ff9bccfa16c7b79acaeba8c25f157","tid":125573,"uid":7768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:55:14.000Z","msg":"新手想學貝多芬悲愴第二樂章會唔會好難？"},{"pid":"22a02a62728b70ad77dddb377703e9b61b61f528","tid":125573,"uid":79114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:56:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新手想學貝多芬悲愴第二樂章會唔會好難？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得唔易，首野雖然d音唔難，但係要捉到個touching唔易"},{"pid":"3f99ea321a662b88f3d4d64ce5e761f02804e998","tid":125573,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:00:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小狗圓舞曲梗係唔係蕭邦最易啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁邊首會易d?<br />\n其實我最鍾意係fantaisie impromptu<br />\n但我應該一世都彈唔到<br />\n所以想學首蕭邦最易的歌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">當貼近一下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小狗圓舞曲同 fantaisie impromptu都唔易wo, 唔好未學行先學走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人覺得夜曲 第2首唔錯，又唔難又好聽</blockquote><br />\n一定係 Funeral March<br />\n但咩歌都都係<br />\n彈岩音唔難 彈岩聲音先係重點"},{"pid":"378a9ce2545b6aca9ea718bcceae182e487c6d24","tid":125573,"uid":79114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:02:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小狗圓舞曲梗係唔係蕭邦最易啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁邊首會易d?<br />\n其實我最鍾意係fantaisie impromptu<br />\n但我應該一世都彈唔到<br />\n所以想學首蕭邦最易的歌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">當貼近一下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小狗圓舞曲同 fantaisie impromptu都唔易wo, 唔好未學行先學走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人覺得夜曲 第2首唔錯，又唔難又好聽</blockquote><br />\n一定係 Funeral March<br />\n但咩歌都都係<br />\n彈岩音唔難 彈岩聲音先係重點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFuneral March都唔難<br />\n但係成首sonata no. 2 簡直係蕭邦 最究極作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"745dea66e068bededff7f9634945ee125ee27db3","tid":125573,"uid":22938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:05:23.000Z","msg":"第一眼睇做成人鋼琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我出返去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7344f82b81a0bee5211f7df9762a92f42b80eebd","tid":125573,"uid":5777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:10:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新手想學貝多芬悲愴第二樂章會唔會好難？</blockquote><br />\n8級架喎 唔學番幾三五七年都有難度<br />\n<br />\n有需要可以搵我學 可上門 tg hin1125<br />\n利申 music degree final year 演奏級 係parsons 同有巴絲都教緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51d4e7a1fff8f98084bc54d609c739d87c59181","tid":125573,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:17:57.000Z","msg":"是咪有成人野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f30c335cc8604c699e578